net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data

Class TreeModelValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.data.TreeModelValidator

  • public class TreeModelValidator
extends Object
    This class will test a TreeModel for adherance to the TreeModel contract and produce a list of issues as String objects that must must be fixed. Please note that the validation methods in this class are expensive.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
